'''Rose Kabuye''' ( yavutse kuya 22 Mata 1961 i Muvumba) Ni umwe mu ba coloneli basezerewe mu [https://www.mod.gov.rw/ igisirikare cy'u Rwanda], aho akiri umugore w'ambere wari ufite ipeti ry'ohejuru mu ngabo z'[[IGIHUGU N'INTORE|igihugu]]. Ubu akora mu bikorera ku giti cyabo aho ari umuyobozi muri kompanyi yitwa Virunga, yigeze no kuba umuyobozi w'[[umujyi wa Kigali]]. Aba ushizwe kugutegura ingendo z'abayobozi bakuru b'igihugu, aza gukora munteko inshinga amategeko. kubera uruhare yagize mu kuhohora igihugu yahawe umudali n' umukuru w'igihugu [[Paul Kagame]]. 

=== UBUZIMA BWITE ===
'''Rose kabuye''' yakuriye kandi yiga muri [[Ubugande|Uganda]], yatangiye amahugurwa ya gisirikare 1986 arangije kwiga muri Kaminuza ya Makerere<ref>https://www.mak.ac.ug/</ref> aho yabonye impamyabushobozi muri politike n'ubuyobozi, yagiye mu ngabo za RPF (Rwandan Patriotic Front) 1980<ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rwandan_Patriotic_Front</ref>, aza nokuba umwe mubayobozi muri izo ngabo, aho yabaye umwe mubagize ibiganiro by 'amahoro hagati ya RPF na goverinoma yu rwanda yahozeho.<ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rose_Kabuye</ref>

